(40, 9, 12, 24, 33, 6, 6, 'need not a physician', 'Healing and Restoration Theme', 'Both passages emphasize the concept of healing, with Matthew highlighting the need for a physician for the sick, while Jeremiah promises health and cure. This connection highlights the theme of divine restoration and the importance of addressing spiritual and physical ailments.', 'theme', 0.377, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
