(40, 9, 12, 19, 147, 3, 3, 'need not a physician', 'Healing of the Brokenhearted', 'This connection highlights the theme of healing in both passages. Matthew emphasizes the need for a physician for the sick, while Psalms speaks of healing the broken in heart.', 'theme', 0.363, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
