(40, 9, 13, 40, 12, 7, 7, 'I will have mercy, and not sacrifice', 'Mercy Over Sacrifice', 'Both passages emphasize the phrase ''I will have mercy, and not sacrifice,'' highlighting the importance of mercy over ritualistic practices. This connection underscores a consistent theme of prioritizing compassion and understanding over mere adherence to the law.', 'theme', 1.0, 'high', 'v1.2', 'gpt-4o-mini'),
